
1st Method
Open Git Bash 
$mkdir ~/test-repo
$cd ~/test-repo 
$git init 
$git remote add origin http://github.com/ysktgw/R-programming.git  ## Connecting local and online copy 

2nd Method 
Fork 
and go to Git Bash                         
$ git clone https://github.com/ysktgw/ForkedReponame.git         ## Cloning repo 


GO TO http://git-scm.com/book/en/Git-Basica-Getting-a-Git-Repository
